reviewText: The favorite of the four was "Two Weeks Notice"  Sandra Bullock and Hugh Grant are hilarious together!  Getting 4 movies for the price of one, who would want to pass that deal up.
summary: Great movie compilation with great savings.

reviewText: This four pack arrived in pristine condition and much earlier than scheduled. It was brand new still in the plastic wrap. I am completely satisfied with them. The price was amazing - I could not have found these movies for this price in stores. I'm very happy.

reviewText: I have enjoyed seeing Sandra Bullock in other movies, however, the witchcraft mumbo-jumbo is not my bag.I'm sorry, but this was also a dud in the bad language department. I couldn't get rid of it fast enough.
